{"tid":1253294,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 民建聯植潔鈴Telegram用游蕙禎做Icon","createTime":"2019-06-23T13:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T10:04:18.000Z","uid":145758,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d68a75d210652a39fd2c9002d939cc68f2cfd16f","tid":1253294,"uid":145758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:21:15.000Z","msg":"通訊軟件Telegram近期廣受港人歡迎，成為組織群眾反修例的主要渠道，Telegram最大好處是用家可隱藏自己的電話號碼，但若其他使用者為該用家的聯絡人，用家身份則沒有隱藏。<br />\n<br />\n因宣誓風波被褫奪議員資格的游蕙禎今天在facebook張貼一張相片，相中顯示，植潔鈴以私人號碼註冊Telegram帳號，用戶名稱為「Marychannn」，不過其個人頭像竟用游蕙禎的相片。<br />\n<br />\n於是，游蕙禎指在今天致電植潔鈴與對方對質，游質問對方為何「偷相」，植解釋相片是從telegram內搜尋到的。<br />\n<br />\n游蕙禎其後質疑對方「扮本土派」，植否認並強調不希望他人有這樣的誤會，<span style=\"color: red;\">她又表示不知相中人是游蕙禎，只是覺得「有啲似樣」和「靚女」，又為引起誤會向游蕙禎致歉。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebLNz9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FebLNz9d.png&h=c8fd3796&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efdc25bf24dd024ea4b227dd18199196c890e902","tid":1253294,"uid":111573,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:22:42.000Z","msg":"當人ON9咩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73675e93fb2772d757c1cbd3a1838e580be6a50","tid":1253294,"uid":230316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"師承鍾樹根唔講得笑呀"},{"pid":"327a64aed352b7625107f2a3a2496a18c827ca37","tid":1253294,"uid":40849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse